{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙与美蚕娘黎明前离开山区前往市集。途中美蚕娘讲述自己十四岁被聘礼换嫁的身世，项少龙对古代风俗感慨万千。抵达市集后，美蚕娘发现已死恶霸焦毒的兄弟在场，惊恐不已。焦毒手下围攻项少龙，项少龙以柴刀和拳脚轻松击败二十多名流氓，赢得围观群众喝彩。收购健马的华服男子陶方赏识项少龙身手，以月薪五十铜钱聘请他为保镖，随马队前往邯郸。项少龙答应并预支二百铜钱给美蚕娘作生活费。二人在营地度过最后一夜后依依惜别，美蚕娘返回桑林村，项少龙随陶方马队踏上前往赵国首都邯郸的路途，开启寻找秦始皇之旅。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "你怎样会嫁给那两兄弟的？你自己的家人在那里呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家住在朝太阳要走三天的地方，有一天他们两兄弟带了十张虎皮、一张熊皮、五十条貂皮、五条牛、一百只羊来向爹换我，这么丰厚的奁是我们族内从未曾听过的，于是我便嫁了给他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "那年你多少岁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "十四岁！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "什么？那还未到合法的欢好年龄呀？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以前赶集最少要走十个时辰，但自从有人建了这条运兵道后，四个时辰便可到达市集，省时多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈！终有适合我的工作了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！我再不能失去你这个丈夫了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看！左边那群汉子就是土霸焦毒的兄弟，他们正盯着我们，怎办才好呢？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "娘子不用慌，有为夫在此，谁也不能伤你半条毫毛。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上马三十铜元！上马三十铜元！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她们都是白夷人，最擅养马，男女都是很好的猎人，没有人敢欺负他们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这些武士都是做走镖的，专门负责替商贾运送财帛，是最赚钱的差事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "在这里杀人是否要坐牢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么是坐牢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "杀人有没有人管？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "除了自己族人外，谁都不会理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不是要和这么多人打架吧？他们都有剑！我们可把换来的钱给他们。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_du_xiong_di",
      "speaker_name": "焦毒兄弟",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "美蚕娘！焦大哥在那里？这臭汉是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jiao_du_xiong_di",
      "text": "你们的焦大哥给宰了，要报仇的便放马过来。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jiao_du_xiong_di",
      "text": "来吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "老天爷！你真是勇武！奴家以后都不怕恶人了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "知道怎样去邯郸了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有人听过这地方，但却不知怎样去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "壮士请留步！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本人陶方，乃乌氏棵大爷手下十二仆头之一，壮士囗音奇怪，不知是何方人士？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "我和贱内都是桑林人，陶爷请我来，不知有什么关照？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "壮士有没有兴趣弄大笔的钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "愿陶爷有以教我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以壮士惊人的身手，真是可以一挡百，若你肯做我的保镖，我可以每月给你五十个铜钱，壮士意下如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那够我们一年的生活了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "这条件很吸引，可是我们还要到邯郸去哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项壮士定是未听过我们乌大爷的威名，他就是邯郸首屈一指的'畜牧大王'，我们在各地收集足够马匹后，便会运往邯郸，壮士若做我的保镖，正是一举两得的美事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "不过我要带她同行呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！我们除了收购健马外，还挑购各山地的美女，所以壮士偕美同行，一点问题都没有。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我使人打扫地方给贤夫妇歇息，换过新衣，明天黎明便回邯郸去，壮士惯用那种武器，若是剑的话，我立即送你一把邯郸陈老铁打造的好剑，刚才你拾的那把可以扔掉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "到邯郸要走多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快马十日可达，但像我们那种走法，沿途又要收购马匹美女，最少要一个月的路程才行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "窦良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄这么本事，有机会倒要领教。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "不用怕那窦良，迟早我会找个机会教训他一顿，什么恶人我项少龙也不害怕。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "城市的人都很奸诈，奴家怕不习惯那种生活。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "有我保护你，怕什么呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "桑林村住的都是好人，生活丰足，一年比一年好，现在焦毒那群恶棍全给打死了，更是太平乐土，夫君！不若我们回到那里居住，快快乐乐直至老死，而奴家则为你生儿育女，不是更好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "不若这样吧！我去向陶方借一百个铜钱，那足够你两年生活费了，而我则到邯郸闯天下，一有成就便回来接你，那不是两全其美吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那不是要和你分开吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "快则几个月，迟则一两年，我定会回来的。别忘记我是老天爷派来，所以绝不会死掉的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    }
  ],
